      "text": "Hold on, please hold on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said, hold on she wasn't back to me and make believe that you carry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I walked actual.",
